text: Blabia colobotheoides is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Thomson in 1864. It is known from Colombia and Peru.BioLib.cz - Blabia colobotheoides. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Blabia Category:Beetles described in 1864
title: Blabia colobotheoides
